msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account. You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration. If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Si aad u isticmaasho adeegyada iibinta badeecadaha Vortem, waxaad u baahan tahay akoon AliExpress. Waxaad ku xidhi karta akoonkaaga ka Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration. Haddii aadan haysan akoon, waxaad si toos ah u iska diiwaan geli kartaa halkaas."

msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account."
msgstr "Si aad u isticmaasho adeegyada iibinta badeecadaha Vortem, waxaad u baahan tahay akoon AliExpress."

msgid "You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration."
msgstr "Waxaad ku xidhi karta akoonkaaga ka Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration."

msgid "If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Haddii aadan haysan akoon, waxaad si toos ah u iska diiwaan geli kartaa halkaas."

