msgstr "Shuruudaha iyo Qawaaniinta"

msgid "1. License Agreement"
msgstr "1. Heshiiska Shatiga"

msgid "By using this plugin, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. The plugin is provided under the GPL v2 or later license."
msgstr "Markaad isticmaalayso plugin-kan, waxaad ogolaatay inaad u hoggaansanto dhammaan sharciyada iyo qawaaniinta khuseeya. Plugin-kan waxaa lagu bixiyaa shatiga GPL v2 ama ka dambeeya."

