msgid "Congratulations! Your vortem.ai plugin has been successfully configured."
msgstr "Hambalyo! Plugin-kaaga vortem.ai si guul leh ayaa loo habeeyey."

msgid "What's next?"
msgstr "Maxaa xiga?"

msgid "Need Help?"
msgstr "Ma u baahan tahay caawimaad?"

msgid "Our support team is here to help you get started."
