msgid "1. authentication Agreement"
msgstr "1. Heshiiska Aqoonsiga"

msgid "By using this plugin, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. The plugin is provided under the GPL v2 or later authentication."
msgstr "Markaad isticmaalayso plugin-kan, waxaad ogolaatay inaad raacdo dhammaan sharciyada. Plugin-kan waxaa lagu bixiyaa aqoonsiga GPL v2 ama ka dambeeya."

msgid "2. Data Usage"
msgstr "2. Isticmaalka Xogta"

msgid "We collect and process data necessary for the operation of the service, including product information, order details, and customer data. All data is handled in accordance with our privacy policy."
msgstr "Waxaan ururinaa oo aan ka shaqeynaa xogta lagama maarmaanka u ah adeegga, oo ay ku jiraan macluumaadka alaabta, faahfaahinta dalabka, iyo xogta macaamiisha. Dhammaan xogta waxaa loo maareeyaa si waafaqsan siyaasadda ilaalinta xogta gaarka ah."

msgid "3. Service Availability"
msgstr "3. Helitaanka Adeegga"

msgid "While we strive to maintain high service availability, we cannot guarantee uninterrupted service. We reserve the right to perform maintenance and updates as needed."
msgstr "In kasta oo aan ku dadaalno in adeeggu had iyo jeer diyaar yahay, ma dammaanad qaadi karno adeeg aan kala go' lahayn."

msgid "4. Support"
msgstr "4. Taageerada"

msgid "Technical support is provided through our support channels. Response times may vary based on the complexity of the issue."
msgstr "Taageerada farsamada waxaa lagu bixiyaa kanaaladayada taageerada. Waqtiga jawaabtu wuu kala duwanaan karaa."

msgid "5. Updates"
msgstr "5. Cusboonaysiinta"

msgid "Plugin updates are provided to improve functionality and security. It is recommended to keep the plugin updated to the latest version."
msgstr "Cusboonaysiinta plugin-ka waxaa loo bixiyaa si loo hagaajiyo shaqada iyo amniga. Waxaa lagula talinayaa in plugin-ka lagu hayo noociisii ugu dambeeyey."

msgid "Enter your Vortem.ai authentication key to activate the plugin and access all features."
msgstr "Gali furaha aqoonsiga Vortem.ai si aad u hawlgeliso plugin-ka oo aad u hesho dhammaan sifooyinka."

msgid "You can find your authentication key in your Vortem.ai account dashboard."
msgstr "Waxaad ka heli kartaa furahaaga aqoonsiga gudaha dashboard-ka akoonkaaga Vortem.ai."

msgid "Need help?"
msgstr "Ma u baahan tahay caawimaad?"

msgid "Complete the setup wizard to configure your authentication and get started."
msgstr "Dhammaystir caawiyaha habaynta si aad u habayso aqoonsigaaga oo aad u bilowdo."

